# What Just Happened?

Let's recap what you installed and why:

| What | Why |
|------|-----|
| **Cursor** | Your code editor with AI assistance |
| **NVM** | Manages different versions of Node.js |
| **Node.js** | Runs JavaScript code outside a browser |
| **npm** | Installs packages (pre-built code you can use) |

You don't need to memorize this. You can always ask the AI to remind you.

