# Troubleshooting

If something goes wrong, don't panic. Just describe the problem to the AI:

{% card title="Prompt: Help Me Fix This" variant="feature" %}
```
Something went wrong and I got this error:

[Paste your error message here]

I'm a beginner. Please:
1. Explain what this error means in simple terms
2. Tell me why it might have happened
3. Walk me through fixing it step by step
4. Explain how to avoid this in the future
```
{% /card %}

{% callout type="tip" title="Errors Are Normal" %}
Every developer sees errors constantly. It's not a sign that you did something wrong—it's just how computers communicate. The AI can help you understand and fix almost any error.
{% /callout %}

